16
00:00:49.815 --> 00:00:54.253
innovation and outreach, and
that freed up a lot of time for

17
00:00:54.286 --> 00:00:56.856
me to work on a number
of different

18
00:00:56.889 --> 00:00:58.891
accessibility initiatives.

19
00:00:58.924 --> 00:01:04.163
So I belong to the ITIC Group,
where they're the people who

20
